<div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
        <form class="form-horizontal">
            <p>Enter the credentials in the space provided below to get started. </p>
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label">{{ _('ORG') }}</label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control input-block-level"
                        data-bind="value: settings.settings.plugins.ulendocaas.ORG">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label">{{ _('ACCESSID') }}</label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <input type="text" class="input-block-level"
                        data-bind="value: settings.settings.plugins.ulendocaas.ACCESSID">
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>It is important to use the provided <b>MACHINEID</b> in order to authenticate your device with our service.</p>
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label">{{ _('MACHINEID') }}</label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <input type="text" class="input-block-level"
                        data-bind="value: settings.settings.plugins.ulendocaas.MACHINEID">
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>Use a useful machine name to identify your machine. This information will be used to sort and identify your machine in the CaaS Central UI.</p>
            <div class="control-group">
                <label class="control-label">{{ _('MACHINENAME') }}</label>
                <div class="controls">
                    <input type="text" class="input-block-level"
                        data-bind="value: settings.settings.plugins.ulendocaas.MACHINENAME">
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>